{
  "stem": "18626.10",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The big shots used to come in, too, you know, and yakety-yak, you know, with the big engineers there about-- talking what they're building.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they are-- they're going to build, you know, the big secret weapon, what they called 'atom bomb.'",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I saw, you know, the terrible things, you know, while they were talking, the, the killings and all the things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Americans, while they interviewed me, they saw that I am good material to testify.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw a lot of people getting killed with my own eyes by these people-- and their names, the people who got killed, and when.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they selected me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said to me, we're going to pick you up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they give you the date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then two weeks later, they came again, and again interviewed me again and looked in the paper to see, you know, if I'll make a witness not to get, you know, confused.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if so, that everything I told them before-- it's almost like you cannot forget troubles when it's in your brain, understand?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It shows that everything is intact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They says, oh, this is going to be a witness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's the youngest witness-- going to be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because most of the witnesses were doctors, lawyers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were prisoners, priests.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But a young boy like me, I felt funny, you know, that I'm going to be a witness, too, between all the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] intellectual, you know, educated, you know, prominent ex-prisoners.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it took again maybe three weeks or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told the people in the hospital they were taking away Moses to the-- Dachau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think he's going to stay maybe there five or six weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
